<bibRefCitation id="52204B4C9A062A14FF3EFC3BFE0BFC36" author="BELLAMY C. L." box="[227,397,944,968]" pageId="23" pageNumber="752" pagination="1 - 626" refId="ref22407" refString="BELLAMY C. L. 2008: A world catalogue and bibliography of the jewel beetles (Coleoptera: Buprestoidea). Volume 1. Introduction; fossil taxa; Schizopodidae; Buprestidae: Julodinae - Chrysochroinae: Poecilonotini. Pensoft Series Faunistica, No. 76, (1 - 2) + 1 - 626 pp." type="book chapter" year="2008">BELLAMY (2008)</bibRefCitation>
